    "The former considers meaningful textual instructions as prompts, as shown in Section III-A1, while the latter uses vectors composed of continuous numerical values as prompts, as shown in Section III-A2.",
    "1) Textual Prompt Optimization: Before the emergence of ChatGPT, several research studies had already explored the use of metaheuristic algorithms, such as EAs, for prompt engineering in pretrained language models.",
